1. *Izuzetno* je bitno da se pridržavamo pravila. (It is exceptionally important to follow the rules.) 
2. On je *izuzetno* uspešan u poslu. (He is exceptionally successful in his job.) 
3. Oni su *izuzetno* usredsredjeni na svoje ciljeve. (They are exceptionally focused on their goals.) 
4. Ovo je *izuzetno* važna informacija. (This is exceptionally important information.) 
5. Ona je *izuzetno* talentovana. (She is exceptionally talented.)